{"tid":219720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國國防部破天荒公開道歉 海軍節圖用咗美艦俄軍機","createTime":"2017-04-27T11:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T14:55:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32773b8ac03170e27d56496b41ee3cdab1592b52","tid":219720,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170427/large/1493285530_8786.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170427%2Flarge%2F1493285530_8786.jpg&h=ba296311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國防部今日例行記者會上，歷史上首次作出公開道歉，承認工作失誤。據悉，這次是中共推行新聞發布會制度以來，國家部委就日常工作失誤，首次作出道歉。<br />\n<br />\n國防部今日例行記者會上，國防部新聞局局長、新聞發言人楊宇軍表示，就4月23日國防部官方微博發了一張圖，該圖片同時出現中國航母、美國軍艦和俄羅斯戰機，即時受到內地網友指責。對此楊宇軍公開致歉：「疏忽在小編，責任領導擔。在此我代表小編團隊，向所有關注、關心和支持我們的粉絲表示誠摯歉意和衷心感謝。」<br />\n海軍節當日，國防部官方微博貼出的海報圖片錯漏百出，海報所見，圖中有三架呈現起飛狀態的殲-10，屬於陸基型戰機、根本不是艦載型，而且更別說能在遼寧號航艦上起降，現解放軍艦載機僅有殲-15戰機。<br />\n有網友又指出，甫從遼寧號航艦滑跳起飛的戰機，除起飛角度有誤外，型號也大錯特錯，有網友指，該戰機是俄羅斯最新一代的米格-35戰機原型機，目前仍處於研發階段，尚未服役且無艦載型號。<br />\n在海報的左上方，有兩艘的補給艦，實際上是美軍的聖安東尼奧級（San Antonio-class）新一代兩棲船塢登陸艦，解放軍根本沒有此艦；「補給艦」前方有兩艘潛艇，其大細比例亦不合符常理。"},{"pid":"6733f574e24b7de7bdeeaf281718f6cbc9821c86","tid":219720,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170427/56621721\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170427%2F56621721&h=6a253cdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8ed8f26ceebf6cb2d550b45d7a79521d4b2168c","tid":219720,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170427/56621721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170427%2F56621721&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8d580832\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170427%2F56621721&h=9266e285\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170427/56621721</a>"},{"pid":"66dd4c6f41d4b8800a09aa7e129aa006d17fb976","tid":219720,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.news.com.au/world/asia/china-released-this-really-badly-photoshopped-picture-of-its-navy-fleet-and-the-internet-unleashed/news-story/e394e048d132813e35cbb771bc924c42?utm_content=SocialFlow&amp;utm_campaign=EditorialSF&amp;utm_source=News.com.au&amp;utm_medium=Facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchina-released-this-really-badly-photoshopped-picture-of-its-navy-fleet-and-the-internet-unleashed%2Fnews-story%2Fe394e048d132813e35cbb771bc924c42%3Futm_content%3DSocialFlow%26utm_campaign%3DEditorialSF%26utm_source%3DNews.com.au%26utm_medium%3DFacebook&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=809d9b64\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.news.com.au/world/asia/china-released-this-really-badly-photoshopped-picture-of-its-navy-fleet-and-the-internet-unleashed/news-story/e394e048d132813e35cbb771bc924c42?utm_content=SocialFlow&amp;utm_campaign=EditorialSF&amp;utm_source=News.com.au&amp;utm_medium=Facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.newsapi.com.au/image/v1/9b94cc2e02372adad608f2e314a9d314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.newsapi.com.au%2Fimage%2Fv1%2F9b94cc2e02372adad608f2e314a9d314&h=1e195123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCHINA&rsquo;S Defence Ministry has apologised for allowing a badly photoshopped picture of navy ships and fighter jets to appear on its social media accounts over the weekend.<br />\nThe dodgy image, which appeared on the ministry&rsquo;s accounts on social networking sites Weibo and Wechat, was meant to mark the navy&rsquo;s 68th birthday.<br />\nIt included fighter jets soaring over the country&rsquo;s first aircraft carrier, with two other warships steaming along in the background, above two ghostly submarines."},{"pid":"14dd9ab85c7d02984b815620872c09f20501f545","tid":219720,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8843343c9428c9d2e5898d1a32ac4194e39683a9","tid":219720,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:03:39.000Z","msg":"張poster設計真係不得了"},{"pid":"304728350d65c7d0b3179b9666d545b81ee8ba97","tid":219720,"uid":66559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:04:23.000Z","msg":"呢個國家on9到咩程度"},{"pid":"82ac93d7a72f343aa3f0b69a2a4e3de2d92fb806","tid":219720,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"小小支那，可笑可笑"},{"pid":"0297e97e571bc6eeda0a17cc8f1c9e476473c3c2","tid":219720,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8f358041ac7ee0faec9e67b07c705e691519f63","tid":219720,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"整poster嗰team人駛唔駛槍斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee46da1bfd9faa9fac96270c754b1f4a65c3dd7","tid":219720,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54Ad2s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54Ad2s.gif&h=e2c265d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ddmM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ddmM.gif&h=c23e421e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/685Y0